2005-12-20 Features of version 0.0.3

	* Visual display of the Tor daemon status (red icon: stopped,
	  green icon: started, dark green icon: sending/receiving);
	* Tooltip with basic informations (daemon status, uptime, 
	  version, bytes sent/received, log warinigs/errors,
	  number of connected onion routers);
	* Menu that allow to start, stop and restart the daemon, and
	  to display an about box and a properties dialog;
	* Properties dialog with informations about daemon activity;
	* GUI for tor-resolve;
	* Support for localization;
	* Italian translation.
